{"tid":2121062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府就洪水橋發展計劃張貼收回土地公告","createTime":"2020-07-23T05:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T05:49:56.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8dbd55664013d7969131f85e6802ca73fa47b0","tid":2121062,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"地政總署今日在洪水橋／厦村新發展區第一期發展計劃工程範圍內將會收回的土地張貼公告，指出有關土地將於公告張貼後三個月，即今年10月24日，需歸還政府所有。政府將會按程序，於張貼收地公告後，向相關的土地業權人提供特惠土地補償。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539420-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539420-20200723.htm&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=5c074b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539420-20200723.htm&h=31769bdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539420-20200723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"717e67ecf2f145cd77f694249aaea7b1fc5232ac","tid":2121062,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"元朗國金塔都收<br />\n肯定賠得好甘"},{"pid":"b0633e57beb78bed127ba8bb2f0fcdacc5436bc3","tid":2121062,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"邊個大孖沙D地"},{"pid":"6574e48e6c2997cce362ff6cb18746237f0b5949","tid":2121062,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"717e67ecf2f145cd77f694249aaea7b1fc5232ac","tid":2121062,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"元朗國金塔都收<br />\n肯定賠得好甘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"大陸收地好似強制性冇得賠"},{"pid":"38aac1966cdc69d4b81fce48335fe9aa304657fb","tid":2121062,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"墳墓都收 大膽了"},{"pid":"8bf17a0d5e4d9528a4e45f3efa0b7a33f753d070","tid":2121062,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"